"-------- General -------"

"Enable syntax hilight
syntax enable

"256 colours, please
set t_Co=256

"Display the line numbers.
set number

colorscheme desert


"-------- Search -------"
"Enables the search hilight
set hlsearch

"Enables the incremental search
set incsearch


"-------- Interactions -------"

"Make backspace behave like every other editor.
set backspace=indent,eol,start
